title: No, Beto O’Rourke Didn’t Promise To ‘Drop My Nudes’ If Texas Goes Blue
subtitle: A TV writer's prank earned an almost immediate Twitter suspension.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Former U.S. Rep. Beto O'Rourke vowed to "drop my nudes" if the state of Texas goes to the Democrats in the 2020 general election.
